      <title>支持对华电动汽车关税的欧盟国家面临最大报复风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/eu-s-yes-votes-on-china-ev-tariffs-seen-as-targets-for-revenge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟决定对中国电动汽车征收关税，人们的焦点转向北京将如何以及何时对欧盟多年来最大的贸易争端升级采取报复措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/eu-s-yes-votes-on-china-ev-tariffs-seen-as-targets-for-revenge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 05:21:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
