    <item>
      <title>中东紧张局势削弱乐观情绪，股市波动：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-after-us-jobs-report-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五公布的就业数据强于预期，导致中东紧张局势减弱了人们对美国经济的乐观情绪，欧洲股市抹去了涨幅，美国股指期货下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-after-us-jobs-report-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:37:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富时指数调整 韩国、印度债券市场备受关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/ftse-s-index-revamp-has-korean-indian-bond-markets-on-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国已尽一切努力将其债券纳入主要的富时罗素指数，而印度则避开了公共改革 — — 但后者在全球投资者中的受欢迎程度可能使其在加入相关基准指数方面具有优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/ftse-s-index-revamp-has-korean-indian-bond-markets-on-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
