      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/oil-bets-are-most-bullish-in-two-years-as-mideast-tension-flares</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，石油期货创下一年多以来的最大涨幅。期权市场的狂热甚至更为强烈。]]></description>
